{"tid":1566061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十萬火急 星期六行動出爐！推上熱門！","createTime":"2019-09-13T11:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:43:37.000Z","uid":167548,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6b37fa87b8676c52e7ef468372a75cb54c8031","tid":1566061,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣 文宣 文宣 9.15！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家好似忽略左其重要性！<br />\n<br />\n呢一個將會是星期日唔會再批遊行嘅里程碑！<br />\n<br />\n呢一個將會是第一個目標百萬人數嘅星期日遊行！<br />\n<br />\n呢一個將會是民陣失去合法號召力嘅再一次肯定！<br />\n<br />\n呢一個將會是試驗願榮光歸香港嘅試金石！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我在此呼籲當你唱起呢首歌，你地就身負責任每一個星期日大遊行你必須出席！<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣東角道見！1500準時！百萬人癱瘓港島！"},{"pid":"933320b4efb2ac80fce7e8fc98f215676eb31a89","tid":1566061,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nfq2cS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfq2cS2.jpg&h=0884baac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EknW1Mn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEknW1Mn.jpg&h=84f580d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba6f50c47e1da9c771cd2da1f56c08ad433da6cd","tid":1566061,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5NoYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5NoYN.jpg&h=6894a64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvUKrb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvUKrb8.jpg&h=ec6b4d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12點英領和平請願<br />\n灰磚範圍 英國領土</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2點打後 自由活動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" c